        <item>
            <title>HUAWEI Pura 70 突發推出，運行 HarmonyOS 4.2、1/1.3 吋感光元件主相機</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/huawei-pura-70/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-pura-70</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/huawei-pura-70/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 05:30:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pura 70]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pura 70 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pura 70 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[華為]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229999</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>華為在未有開發布會的情況下，今（18 日）突然推出「HUAWEI Pura 70 系列，先鋒計劃」，Pura 70、70 Pro、70 Pro+、70 Ultra 四個機款將會登場，售價由 5,499 人民幣（約 6,070 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港元</span>）起。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1230004 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-4-694x197.png" alt="" width="694" height="197" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-4-694x197.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-4.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1230001 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-1-694x199.png" alt="" width="694" height="199" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-1-694x199.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1230002 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-2-694x198.png" alt="" width="694" height="198" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-2-694x198.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1230003 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-3-694x198.png" alt="" width="694" height="198" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-3-694x198.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-3.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲華為推出 Pura 70、Pura 70 Pro、Pura 70 Pro+ 及 Pura 70 Ultra，售價由 5,499 人民幣（約 6,070 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港元</span>）起。</p><p>華為 Pura 70、Pura 70 Pro、Pura 70 Pro+ 及 Pura 70 Ultra 的設計獨特，圓角三角形的相機外觀具辨識度。Ultra 型號擁有星芒底紋，而 Pro+ 亦有光織格紋。Pura 70 使用 6.6 吋的 OLED 螢幕，其餘三機則是 6.8 吋，四部新機的解析度及刷新率均有 FHD+ 和 120Hz。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1230009 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-8-655x580.png" alt="" width="655" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-8-655x580.png 655w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-8.png 1016w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 655px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Ultra 型號擁有星芒底紋</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1230007 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-6-688x580.png" alt="" width="688" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-6-688x580.png 688w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-6.png 1048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 688px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Pro+ 亦有光織格紋</p><p>Pura 70 Ultra 坐擁 4000 萬像素 f/2.2 光圈超廣角相機及 5000 萬像素 f/2.1 光圈，OIS 光學防手震超聚光微距長焦相機，可處理 200X 數碼變焦拍攝，並使用了 1 吋感光元件，支援感光元件移位防震功能。 f/1.6-f/4.0 光圈鏡頭首次加入旋轉伸縮鏡頭結構，使用時會出現機械聲音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1230008 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-7-643x580.png" alt="" width="643" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-7-643x580.png 643w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-7.png 997w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 643px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Pura 70 Ultra 坐擁 4000 萬像素 f/2.2 光圈超廣角相機及 5000 萬像素 f/2.1 光圈，OIS 光學防手震超聚光微距長焦相機</p><p>華為 Pura 70、Pura 70 Pro、Pura 70 Pro+ 及 Pura 70 Ultra，定價分別為 5,499 人民幣（約 6,070 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港元</span>）、6,499 人民幣（約 7,173 港元）、7,999 人民幣（約 8,656 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港元</span>）及 9,999 人民幣（約 10,820 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港元</span>）。Pro 和 Ultra 即日起在中國開賣，其餘兩款則要等到 4 月 22 日才有售。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.vmall.com/product/10086821546239.html">Vmall</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/15/matebook-x-pro/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">華為 AI 手提電腦配備 Intel 先進晶片，美國議員表示不可接受</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/richard-yu-huawei-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">華為餘承東自主不再講「遙遙領先」   中國網民表示不習慣</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/10/toyota-huawei-monenta-sign-agreement/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">豐田、華為、Momenta 合作，研發智能駕駛輔助系統</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/huawei-pura-70/mobile-phone/">HUAWEI Pura 70 突發推出，運行 HarmonyOS 4.2、1/1.3 吋感光元件主相機</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
