        </item>
        <item>
            <title>新 X 用戶等 3 個月才可發文，兩國試新制度打擊 AI 假帳戶</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/x-need-to-pay-to-post/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=x-need-to-pay-to-post</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/x-need-to-pay-to-post/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:30:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交網絡]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Twitter]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[x]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229946</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>AI 發展一日千里，為大家生活帶來方便之餘，亦帶來不少資訊安全問題。Elon Musk 近日表示， X 擬在紐西蘭及菲律賓測試新收費制度，用戶如申請帳戶後要立即發文需要繳付 1 美元（約港幣 7.8 元），或者等候 3 個月方能夠發文。</p><p>Elon Musk 在 X 證實將會對新用戶徵費。Elon Musk 指，現今 AI 技術日益先進，甚至破解了以往「機械人認證」，因此將會徵收「小額費用」。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Unfortunately, a small fee for new user write access is the only way to curb the relentless onslaught of bots. </p><p>Current AI (and troll farms) can pass 「are you a bot」 with ease.</p><p>&mdash; Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1779930065469383166?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 15, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>Elon Musk 另外回覆指，用戶亦可選擇不付費，但開設帳戶頭 3 個月沒有發文權限，僅能夠瀏覽帖文，要等 3 個月期限後方能夠發文及回覆。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">That is way harder than paying a tiny fee. </p><p>This is only for new users. They will be able to do write actions for free after 3 months.</p><p>&mdash; Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1779939517278957714?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 15, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/jul/31/x-sign-lights-san-francisco-twitter-office-removed">The Guardian</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.cool3c.com/article/214120">Cool3c</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/15/vivo-x-fold3-pro-china-version-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】vivo X Fold3 Pro 國行，外形　手感　鉸位　功能　主副屏幕　相機　效能開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/14/xs-premium-users-can-no-longer-hide-their-blue-checks/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">X 將移除隱藏「藍剔」功能　Elon Musk 接管 Twitter 時曾引起爭議</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/11/microsoft-ai-pc-event-20-may/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Microsoft 下月舉辦 AI PC 活動，力推 Snapdragon X Elite 筆電</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/x-need-to-pay-to-post/life-tech/social-network/">新 X 用戶等 3 個月才可發文，兩國試新制度打擊 AI 假帳戶</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/x-need-to-pay-to-post/life-tech/social-network/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
