            <title>疑有 DSE 監考員小紅書泄答題簿，考評局：會報警處理</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/dse-xiaohongshu-leakage/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dse-xiaohongshu-leakage</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/dse-xiaohongshu-leakage/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 10:30:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[dse]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小紅書]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229940</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>上週六（13 日）DSE 英文聆聽已經開考，網上流傳有監考人員將相關試卷的試題答題庫上傳至中國社交平台「小紅書」。據《明報》引述考評局指，當局正嚴肅跟進相關事件，將會報警處理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229942" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436166096_1221405133-579x580.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436166096_1221405133-579x580.jpg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436166096_1221405133.jpg 899w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436166096_1221405133-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=122140513370146904&amp;set=pcb.122140513436146904">教育刺針</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229943" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437536834_1221405133-579x580.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437536834_1221405133-579x580.jpg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437536834_1221405133.jpg 899w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437536834_1221405133-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=122140513370146904&amp;set=pcb.122140513436146904">教育刺針</a></p><p>Facebook 專頁「教育刺針」日前發文指，有人將考生不可攜帶離場的 question-answer book （試題答題簿，考生必須交回且不可攜帶離開）內容上傳至小紅書。涉事答題簿為本年度 DSE 英文聆聽卷答題簿，小紅書用戶「Ms.Lucy」將該空白答題簿打上「Ms.Lucy」水印後上傳至小紅書，並附以評語：「監考結束，大家進來看看考的怎樣？」。小紅書用戶「Ms.Lucy」自稱學歷樹仁本科，於港大就讀碩士，現職中學中文教師。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229941" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437387182_1221405133-579x580.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437387182_1221405133-579x580.jpg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437387182_1221405133.jpg 898w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437387182_1221405133-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=122140513370146904&amp;set=pcb.122140513436146904">教育刺針</a></p><p>《明報》就事件查詢考評局，考評局回覆指會嚴肅跟進未經許可轉載試題一事，將會交由警方處理，如有考務人員違反保密規定，將會按照規定採取行動。據《明報》引述《香港考試及評核局條例》指，未經局方批准，不得將試題內容轉載或刊登。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20240417/s00002/1713291913694/">明報</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=122140513370146904&amp;set=pcb.122140513436146904">教育刺針</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/12/dse-2/software/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">DSE 監考員仍未能登入「監考易」　今日續需人手點名</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/11/dse/software/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">DSE「監考易」App 失靈　監考員須改用人手核對考生身份</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/dse-xiaohongshu-leakage/fun-tech/">疑有 DSE 監考員小紅書泄答題簿，考評局：會報警處理</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
